# Decision Records

This directory stores all team decisions for learning and analysis.

Each decision is logged as a JSON file following the schema defined in self-evolution-framework.md.

## Structure

```
decisions/
├── 2026-03-03-dec-001.json
├── 2026-03-03-dec-002.json
└── ...
```

## Purpose

- Track all significant decisions
- Enable pattern recognition
- Support adaptive learning
- Provide audit trail
- Facilitate continuous improvement
